Cold Open: Drone footage of the $3.6 billion expansion site in Nevada. It’s a 4-million-square-foot extension of the original "Diamond." We see the massive foundations for the 100-GWh 4680 cell factory.  
Narrative Arc: The Semi and the Battery  
